  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Membranous nephropathy

          -  Serum creatinine (Screat)&gt; 1,5 mg/dl or ECC &lt; 70 ml/min or increase Screat &gt; 50%

          -  Proteinuria &gt; 2 g/day

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Systemic diseases

          -  Pregnancy wish

          -  Active infection

          -  Liver dysfunction

          -  Abnormal hematology lab

          -  Unstable angina

          -  Nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory agents (NSAIDs)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
